        {
            "title": "黑芝麻智能配股認購方改變",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">黑芝麻智能(02533)公布，1月8 日訂立的配股協議，與認購C方的配售協議終止，改為向配予Shanghai Daixu Venture Capital Parnershi配售856.3萬股。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Shanghai Daixu Venture Capital Parnershi由戴思元實益擁有。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">配售完成後，董事長、執行董事及首席執行官單記章持股13.6%，戴思元持股4.57%，另一認購者嘉興信燦股6.85%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">公司月初公布配股，配股價18.88元，較上交易日聯交所收市價每股21.76元折讓約13.24%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15611408-%e9%bb%91%e8%8a%9d%e9%ba%bb%e6%99%ba%e8%83%bd%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1%e8%aa%8d%e8%b3%bc%e6%96%b9%e6%94%b9%e8%ae%8a",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20251203_FI_source-web_02533-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-26 08:52:39",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "瑞和數智折讓近14%配股籌1.24億元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">瑞和數智(03680)公布，擬配股集資約1.24億元；配股價0.783元，較該股上周五收市價0.91元折讓約13.96%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"瑞和數智官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/03680-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"瑞和數智官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/03680-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">瑞和數智官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">以該股前5個交易日平均收迌價0.978元計，配股價較之折讓19.94%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">集資所得淨額約1.23億元，約70%用於償還借款及補充一般營運資金，餘下約30%用於戰略投資，但不包括直接或間接投資於加密貨幣或其他基於加密貨幣的資產投資。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15611407-%e7%91%9e%e5%92%8c%e6%95%b8%e6%99%ba%e6%8a%98%e8%ae%93%e8%bf%9114%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1%e7%b1%8c1-24%e5%84%84%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/03680-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-26 08:45:37",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "昇能折讓17.82%配股籌1890萬元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">昇能集團(02459)公布，擬配股集資約1890萬元；配股價0.083元，較該股上周五收市價0.101元折讓17.82%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"昇能集團官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/02459-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"昇能集團官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/02459-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">昇能集團官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">若以該股前5個交易日平均收市價0.1034元計，配股價較之折讓9.73%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">集資淨額約1840萬元，約50%用於發展石墨電極業務，包括但不限於採購原材料及石墨電極、支付分包及轉換成本及其他經營及管理費用；約50%將用於補充流動資金及作一般企業用途。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15611397-%e6%98%87%e8%83%bd%e6%8a%98%e8%ae%9317-82%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1%e7%b1%8c1890%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83",
